  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink92-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">niṉakku varaintu tarutaṟkuk kuṟai niṉ tamar aṅku vantu kūṟāmaiyē eṉat tōḻi
          kūṟiṉāḷāka,
          talaimakaḷ mukanōkki ivaḷ kuṟippiṉāl kūṟiṉāḷ eṉpatu aṟinta talaimakaṉ, ‘varaivu
          māṭcimaippaṭiṉ nāṉē varuval’ eṉat talaimakaṭkuc colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink92">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>karuṅkōṭ ṭerumaic ceṅkaṭ puṉiṟṟāk</l>
          <l>kātaṟ kuḻavik kūṟumulai maṭukku</l>
          <l>nuntai nummūr varutu</l>
          <l>moṇṭoṭi maṭantai niṉṉaiyām peṟiṉē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

<l>           We shall come to your village, to your father['s place], </l> 
<l rend="indent4"> 	where they drink from the teat </l> 
<l rend="indent4"> 	of a newly delivered female buffalo </l> 
<l rend="indent4"> 	with black horns and red eyes  </l> 
<l rend="indent4"> 	trickling [milk] for the beloved calf – </l> 
<p/>
<l> If we win you, o bright-bangled girl. </l> 


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
